style=\"color:#059669;\">(4/5)</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:4px 0 0;color:#374151;font-size:11px;line-height:1.5;\">High-NA EUV monopoly, TSMC 2nm ramp orders Q3 2026. Upstream from TSM and NVDA in the foundry chain &#8212; captures capex supercycle without Taiwan tail risk. ~26x fwd P/E vs NVDA ~40x.</p>\n  </td></tr>\n  <tr><td style=\"padding:10px 14px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0;color:#111827;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;\">3. QCOM &#8212; Valuation &#10003; | Financial Strength &#10003; | Catalyst &#10003; <span style=\"color:#059669;\">(3/5)</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:4px 0 0;color:#374151;font-size:11px;line-height:1.5;\">~15x fwd P/E &#8212; cheapest quality semi in the halal universe. AI edge computing ramp H2 2026 complements your data-center-heavy book with a different angle.</p>\n  </td></tr>\n  </table>\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;color:#374151;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;\">Portfolio Risk Scores</p>\n  <table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse;\">\n  <tr style=\"background-color:#f9fafb;\">\n    <th style=\"padding:6px 10px;text-align:left;font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;font-weight:600;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;\">TICKER</th>\n    <th style=\"padding:6px 10px;text-align:center;font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;font-weight:600;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;\">SCORE</th>\n    <th style=\"padding:6px 10px;text-align:center;font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;font-weight:600;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;\">LABEL</th>\n    <th style=\"padding:6px 10px;text-align:left;font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;font-weight:600;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;\">KEY DRIVER</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;\"><td style=\"padding:7px 10px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;\">NVDA</td><td style=\"padding:7px 10px;text-align:center;font-size:12px;\">37/100</td><td style=\"padding:7px 10px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"background:#fef3c7;color:#d97706;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;pad